title: What Happened to Fiona Goode's Soul? Theory Video
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: This theory actually makes a lot of sense! I was a little bit confused with the “You have no soul” line, I thought it was just weak writing. But I should have expected more from Ahs. Thank you for the theory!

I think this theory makes a lot of sense because I don’t know if the witches have no souls theory was right so her making this deal and losing her soul to the axeman is the only reasonable explanation I could think of
They gotta mention Fiona in s8, she was just too important.
Mary:  that makes total sense. I’ve never realized this before, & I’ve seen Coven numerous times.  You rock!

Soooo glad that Jessica Lange is back #1 but best of all is #2 she will be playing CONSTANCE LANGDON!! Every time constance starts a epic monologue my eyes cant leave the screen. Constance gave me chills watching her scenes shes that damn good! AHS isnt AHS without Jessica Lange, Ryan was smart to bring her back.
